text: Emily Shaw or Emily Alice Shaw is a Canadian luthier, classical guitarist and teacher from Ottawa, Ontario. \- \- \- \- As a luthier, she builds classical guitars, baroque guitars ukuleles and similar instruments. \- \- \- \- \- \- \- \- ==References== Category:Luthiers Category:Canadian classical guitarists Category:Canadian women guitarists Category:Canadian musical instrument makers Category:Living people Category:21st-century Canadian guitarists Category:21st-century women musicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
